item.title: Where to find parts?
item.description: It can be pretty difficult to search for some parts on different stores so let’s try to compile a bunch of links to common parts at different stores here. 3.5mm mono jacks LCSC XKB Connectivity PJ-301M-2-B Reichelt CLIFF FC6812 JYO-35 LUMBERG 1502-03 this one is a bit different to the others Tayda A-865 PJ-3001F (A-2563) these have through-hole pins and are good for soldering on to PCBs Thonk Thonkiconn (PJ398SM) 3.
